	('dea2658c-a9c3-4dfd-837b-e3e06e413a08', 'Asylum family reunification', 'https://ind.nl/en/residence-permits/asylum/asylum-family-reunification', '{"category": "residence-permits/asylum", "elements": [{"text": "Asylum family reunification", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Last update: 28 January 2026", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "You have an asylum residence permit and you want to apply for family reunification. Read how you apply for a residence permit and visa (MVV) for family reunification.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Video", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Requirements, process and costs", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Documents", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Application forms", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appointment family reunification of refugees IND", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "The residence permit", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "See also", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Video", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Watch the video ''How do I apply for family reunification if I have been granted asylum in the Netherlands?’", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Show details Hide details", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Arabic subtitles (عربي)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "شاهد الفيلم المتحرك \"كيف أقدّم طلب لم شمل الأسرة إذا حصلت على اللجوء في هولندا؟\" مع ترجمة باللغة العربية.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Dari subtitles (زبان دری)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "فیلم انیمیشن ''چگونه درخواست الحاق فامیل را بدهم اگر به من پناهندگی در هالند داده شده است؟'' را با زیرنویس دری مشاهده کنید.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Somali subtitles (Soomaali)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Daawo muuqaalka ''Sideen u codsadaa mideynta qoyska haddii la i siiyay magangalyo dalka Nederlaan?'' oo leh cinwaan-hoosaadyo Soomaali ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Tigrinya subtitles (ትግሪኛ።)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "\"ኣብ ኔዘርላንድ ዑቕባ እንተድኣ ተዋሂቡኒ ብኸመይ ምጥርናፍ ስድራ-ቤት የመልክት?\" ዝብል ኣርእስቲ ዘለዎ ቪድዮ ተኸታተሉ። ምስ ትግርኛ ትሕዝቶ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Turkish subtitles (Türkçe)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "‘Hollanda''da iltica hakkı aldıysam, aile birleşimi başvurusunu nasıl yaparım?’ başlıklı videoyu Türkçe altyazılı izleyin.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "00:00", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Requirements, process and costs", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "The application process for the residence permit consists of the following steps:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Show details Hide details", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Check requirements", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "This application is only for family reunification. You can only submit this application for your family members if you have an asylum residence permit.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "The following requirements apply to you and your family member:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Asylum residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You have received your asylum residence permit from the Immigration and Naturalization Service (IND).", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Apply within 3 months", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You have to apply for family reunification within 3 months after you have received your asylum residence permit. This is the family reunification period. This period begins from the moment you receive a positive decision on your asylum application.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Family relationship", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member is part of your family. Your family member was also part of your family before you entered the Netherlands.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "No danger to public order or national security", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You do not pose a danger to public order or national security. Everyone aged 12 years or older must completely fill in an Appendix Antecedents Certificate and enclose it with the application. In this certificate you indicate whether you have ever committed an offence or crime.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601 (PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Declaration sponsor", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You declare that you are a sponsor for your family member in the application form. The sponsor is the person who brings the family member to the Netherlands.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "2. Collect documents", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Gather all your documents before submitting your application. You send copies of the documents with your application. The IND will need to examine some documents. These are documents that prove family ties, such as a birth certificate or marriage certificate. Therefore, it is important that your documents are already in the Netherlands when you submit your application.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Once the IND has received your application, you will receive a letter (confirmation of receipt). An appendix is enclosed with this confirmation that you must use to send these original documents. Do not send an original passport or identity card of your family member.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Have official foreign documents translated into Dutch, English, French, or German. The translator must have been sworn in by a Dutch court. You can search for a sworn translator on the website www.bureauwbtv.nl (only available in Dutch).", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Apply", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "3. Apply", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "The IND prefers that you submit the application for your family member. You apply for the MVV and the residence permit at the same time. You can apply online or by post.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Your family member may also apply themselves at the Dutch embassy or consulate abroad.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "4. Pay for application", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Adult applicant", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You were 18 years or older when you applied for asylum. Are you applying for your partner or (foster) child? Then the application is free. Are you applying for other family members? The application costs € 254,00", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Minor applicant", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You were under 18 and unaccompanied when you applied for asylum. Are you applying for your biological parent(s)? The application is free. Are you applying for other family members? The application costs € 254,00", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "For all fees and exceptions, visit our web page Fees: Costs of an application.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "5. Wait for the decision on the application", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "The IND must take a decision within 9 months.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "We can extend the decision period if it takes longer to decide. For example, because the application is not complete. In that case, the IND will send a message.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Follow the application in My IND.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Sometimes more investigation is needed", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Does your family member have no, or not enough documents? Then the IND may carry out more investigation. For example, a DNA test or an interview with you and with your family member. Is more investigation needed? Then, you will receive a letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "When your application is processed", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "When the IND starts with your application depends on the date of your application. And it depends on the family members for whom you applied for family reunification. You can find the average processing time on the page When will the IND start with my application for family reunification?", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "6. Decision on the application", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You will receive the decision in a letter. The decision will be positive or negative.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Positive decision: your family member will get an MVV.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Negative decision: your family member will not get an MVV. You can object against this decision.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "7. Make appointment for MVV visa sticker and travel to the Netherlands", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member can travel to the Netherlands with the MVV.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Collect MVV within 3 months of decision", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "To collect the MVV your family member has to make an appointment at the Dutch representation. This is the embassy or consulate that you filled in on the application form. Your family member has to collect the MVV within 3 months after the IND has taken a decision on your application. This can be extended to 6 months.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Biometrics", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member must provide biometric data during the appointment at the Dutch representation. Your family member will put a signature and the Dutch representation will take fingerprints. Your family member also needs to bring 1 new passport photo. Go to netherlandsworldwide.nl for information on requirements for ID photos.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Valid passport required", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member''s passport must be valid for at least another 6 months when the Dutch representation places the MVV visa sticker in the passport. The MVV is valid for 90 days.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "8. Registration in the Netherlands", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member must travel to the Netherlands within 90 days. After arriving in the Netherlands, your family member reports within 3 days to the IND for registration at the IND. This is only possible by appointment.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Process registration of family members of refugees", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "During the registration, the following happens:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "The IND checks your family member’s identity, MVV and passport or laissez-passer details.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Your family member has provided their photo, signature and fingerprints at the Dutch representation. The IND checks if these data are correct. Sometimes your family member must have their data taken again.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Your family member receives the decision from the IND. And we will have the residence permit (residence document) made. Your family member will receive a letter when the residence permit is ready at the IND desk. The residence permit can only be collected by appointment.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Do you not have suitable housing for yourself and your family member? If so, the municipality will register your family member in the Personal Records Database (in Dutch: Basisregistratie Personen or BRP) on the day of the appointment at the IND. Do you have suitable housing for yourself and your family member? Then your family member will receive a letter at the IND desk with an appointment at the municipality. This will allow your family member to later register with the municipality in the BRP.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Your family member will have to do a tuberculosis (TB) test if necessary. This test will take place at the reception of the Central Agency for the Reception of Asylum Seekers (in Dutch: Centraal Orgaan opvang asielzoekers or COA). Is this not possible or is your family member not staying in a reception centre? Then your family member must make an appointment for a TB test at the public health service (in Dutch: Gemeentelijke Gezondheidsdienst or GGD). It depends on your family member’s nationality whether a TB test is required. Read the following appendix to see if your family member does not need the TB test:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test 7644(PDF, 113.56 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Below you''ll find the documents you need for your application, such as a passport or marriage certificate. The exact documents you need to submit depend on your age at the time of your asylum application.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Adult applicant: documents required for family reunification", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Were you over 18 when you applied for asylum? Read below to find out which documents and attachments you must send with your application for each family member.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Show details Hide details", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your partner", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying for family reunification with your partner:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your partner''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your partner. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your relationship. For example a marriage certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appendix Questionnaire family relationship (married) partner for asylum in connection with family reunification 7646(PDF, 143.05 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your children", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying for family reunification with your children:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your child''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your child. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your family relationship. For example a birth certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Application for DNA test in case of family reunification 7631(PDF, 216.68 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is your child 12 years or older? Please send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Is your child 15 years or older? Please send the following appendices:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Questionnaire family relationship child 7647(PDF, 292.12 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of civil status 7609(PDF, 173.91 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Extra documents if a parent is not travelling with your child", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of the parent remaining behind.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A means of evidence showing the family relationship between the child and the parent remaining behind. For example a birth certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "The parent must give permission for your child to travel to the Netherlands. Please include the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of the parent remaining behind 7148(PDF, 148.7 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is the parent unable to give permission? Please include the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Statement regarding the absence of the Declaration of consent of the parent remaining behind 7649(PDF, 144.79 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Extra documents for a foster child", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of the biological parents of your foster child.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A means of evidence showing the family relationship between the child and the biological parents of the child. For example a birth certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Have the biological parents of your foster child died? Please include a copy of a means of evidence showing that you are the guardian of your foster child. Also include the death certificates of the biological parents of your foster child.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your other family members", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying family reunification for other family members:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your family member''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your family member. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your family relationship.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Questionnaire ‘Family life 8 ECHR’ 7671(PDF, 142.25 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is your family member 12 years or older? Please send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Does your family member have the nationality of 1 of the countries not stated in the ''Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test''? Please include the ''Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test''.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test 7644(PDF, 113.56 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test 7603(PDF, 215.33 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Underage applicant: documents required for family reunification", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Were you under 18 when you applied for asylum? Read below to find out which documents and attachments you must send with your application for each family member.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Show details Hide details", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your parents", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying for family reunification with your parents:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing who your guardian is in the Netherlands if you are under 18 years old during the family reunification application.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your parent''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your parent. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your family relationship. For example a birth certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appendix Application for DNA test in case of family reunification 7631(PDF, 216.68 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your brothers or sisters", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying for family reunification with your brothers or sisters:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing who your guardian is in the Netherlands if you are under 18 years old during the family reunification application.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your brother or sister''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your brother or sister. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your family relationship.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Questionnaire brother or sister in case of family reunification and 8 ECHR 7677(PDF, 146.76 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appendix Application for DNA test in case of family reunification 7631(PDF, 216.68 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is your brother or sister 15 years or older? Please send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of civil status 7609(PDF, 173.91 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Is your brother or sister 12 years or older? Please send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Does your brother or sister have the nationality of 1 of the countries not stated in the ''Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test''? Please include the ''Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test''.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test 7644(PDF, 113.56 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test 7603(PDF, 215.33 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Extra documents if a parent is not traveling with your brother or sister", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of the parent remaining behind.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A means of evidence showing the family relationship between your brother or sister and the parent remaining behind. For example a birth certificate.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "The parent must give permission for your brother or sister to travel to the Netherlands. Please include the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of the parent remaining behind 7148(PDF, 148.7 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is the parent unable to give permission? Please include the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Statement regarding the absence of the Declaration of consent of the parent remaining behind 7649(PDF, 144.79 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents required when applying for your other family members", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Please send the following documents and appendices when applying for family reunification with other family members:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing who your guardian is in the Netherlands if you are under 18 years old during the family reunification application.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A recent and clear photo of your family member''s face.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "A copy of a means of evidence showing the identity of your family member. For example a passport or an identity card.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "An original means of evidence showing your family relationship.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Questionnaire ‘Family life 8 ECHR’ 7671(PDF, 142.25 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Are you applying online? Please also send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Signature Upload (Regular Provisional Residence Permit- persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker) 7653(PDF, 69.19 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Is your family member 12 years or older? Please send the following appendix:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Antecedents Certificate 7601(PDF, 159.54 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Does your family member have the nationality of 1 of the countries not stated in the ''Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test''? Please include the ''Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test''.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appendix Exemption from the obligation to undergo a tuberculosis (TB) test 7644(PDF, 113.56 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Appendix Declaration of intent to undergo a TB test 7603(PDF, 215.33 KB)", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Completing your application", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Did you apply for family reunification and are there any documents missing from your application? Please complete your application as soon as possible. Read how to send copies of documents on the page Submitting additional documents. You can only send original documents with a form that is included with the receipt confirmation. Do you no longer have the receipt confirmation? Then ask your contact person at VWN or Nidos for help.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Documents per country", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Most applicants for family reunification come from the following 6 countries:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Syria", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Eritrea", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Somalia", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Yemen", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Afghanistan", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Turkey", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Are you from one of these countries? Then check your country to see which documents you can submit to prove your identity and family relationship.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "The documents are divided into 3 groups:", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Documents from this group are the best evidence. The IND will likely not need to conduct further research into your identity or family relationship. If you no longer have the documents from group 1, please send as many documents from groups 2 or 3 as possible. The IND will likely need to conduct further research into your identity and family relationship. If you no longer have the document from group 1, please send as many documents from groups 2 or 3 as possible. The IND will likely need to conduct further research into your identity and family relationship.", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Assessment of documents", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Send as many documents as possible. The more documents the IND has, the better they can assess your application. The IND will review all the information you submit. Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Sometimes there are no documents in group 1. In that case, send as many documents from groups 2 and 3 as possible. Do you not have any documents from groups 1, 2, and 3, but you do have other documents? Then send these documents as well. Always send a copy of your passport if you have one.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Difference between a certificate and an extract", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "A certificate is an original document that you receive on the day you get married or on the day you register your child''s birth. You can request an extract from the register of your marriage or birth afterwards.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Additional research", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "If you have insufficient documentation and a valid reason, the IND may initiate additional research. If the IND decides to conduct additional research, you will receive a letter. This letter will explain what research the IND will conduct, such as DNA testing or an interview with you and/or your family member. If you have insufficient or no documentation and no valid reason, the IND may also decide not to conduct additional research. In that case, your application will be rejected.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Show details Hide details", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Syria (سوريا )", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "عند تقديم طلبك، أرسل نُسخًا من المستندات فقط. يجب عليك إرسال المستندات الأصلية بعد أن تتلقى دائرة الهجرة والتجنيس (IND) طلبك. بعد ذلك ستتلقى رسالة (تأكيد استلام) مرفقة بتعليمات حول كيفية إرسال المستندات الأصلية.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "الهوية", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُثبت هوية أحد أفراد عائلتك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة البطاقة الوطنية التركية (كملك) بطاقة الهوية السورية رخصة القيادة صورة قيد مدني فردي الدفتر العسكري جواز السفر", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الزوج أو شريك الحياة", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أنك متزوج أو أنك عشت مع شريكك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة دليل على أنك كنت تعيش مع شريكك صور من حفل الزواج عقد زواج شرعي وثيقة تثبيت الزواج أو تصديقه من المحكمة الشرعية بيان زواج عقد زواج رسمي دفتر العائلة", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الوالدان", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أنك ابن أو ابنة والديك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة شهادة ميلاد صادرة عن المستشفى مستخرج من السجلّ العائلي مستخرج من سجلّ المواليد دفتر العائلة شهادة الميلاد", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الأطفال (أو الأطفال تحت الوصاية) أو الإخوة والأخوات", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أن لديك أطفالًا أو إخوة وأخوات.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة شهادة ميلاد صادرة عن المستشفى بالنسبة لطفل متبنّى أو طفل تحت الوصاية: وثيقة التبنّي / وثيقة الوصاية مستخرج من السجلّ العائلي مستخرج من سجلّ المواليد دفتر العائلة شهادة الميلاد", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الوالد أو الوالدان المتوفّيان للطفل (أو الطفل تحت الوصاية)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "لا تحتاج إلى إرسال هذه الوثائق إلا في حال كان أحد الوالدين أو كلاهما متوفّيان للطفل (تحت الوصاية).", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة مستخرج من سجل الوفيات شهادة الوفاة", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الخدمة العسكرية", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أن أحد أفراد أسرتك يؤدي الخدمة العسكرية أو سبق له أداؤها.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3. تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة شهادة التسريح من الخدمة العسكرية دفتر الخدمة العسكرية", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Eritrea (ኤርትራ)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ምስ መመልከቲኻ ናይ ሰነዳት ቅዳሓት ጥራይ ኣተሓሒዝካ ለኣኽ። መመልከቲኻ ንIND ምስ በጽሖ ኢኻ ነቶም ኦርጅናል ሰነዳት ክትልእኮም ዘለካ። ሽዕኡ ነቶም ኦርጅናል ሰነዳት ክትልእከሉ እትኽእል ጥብቆ ዘለዎ ደብዳቤ (ናይ ምቕባል መረጋገጺ) ክመጽኣካ እዩ።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "መንነት", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "መንነት ኣባል ስድራ-ቤትካ ዘረጋግጹ ሰነዳት።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቐጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ፓስፖርት ካብ 18 ዓመት ዕድመ ጀሚሩ፡ መንነት ወረቐት ፍቓድ መዘወሪ መኪና መንበሪ ካርድ / ናይ ነባርነት ካርድ ናይ ወተሃደር መንቀሳቀሲ ወረቐት (መንቃሳቀሲ) ትሕቲ 18 ዓመት ንዝኾኑ ቆልዑት፡ ናይ ቤት ትምህርቲ ካርድ / ናይ ተማሃራይ መንነት ወረቐት (ታሴራ) ትሕቲ 18 ዓመት ንዝኾኑ ቆልዑት፡ ናይ ቤት-ትምህርቲ ባጀላ ናይ ክብደት ካርድ", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "ካብ ጉጅለ 1 (ደጊም) ዝኾነ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ወይ ደጊም ፈጺሙ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ስለዚ እዚ ንምንታይ ከምኡ ምዃኑ ኣብ ሓደ ፍሉይ ደብዳቤ ግለጽ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "በዓል-ቤት/በዓልቲ-ቤት ወይ መጻምድቲ", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ምስ በዓልቲ-ቤትካ ከም ዝተመርዓኻ ወይ ምስ መጻምድትኻ ብሓባር ትነብር ከም ዝነበርካ ዘርእዩ ሰነዳት።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቕጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን ናይ ቤተ-ክርስቲያን ናይ መርዓ ምስክር ወረቐት ናይ ቃል-ኪዳን ምዝገባ ክብረ-መዝገብ ናይ ቃል-ኪዳን ምስክር ወረቐት ምስ መጻምድትኻ ብሓባር ትነብር ከም ዝነበርካ ዘርእይ መረጋገጺ ናይ መርዓኹም ስእልታት", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "(ደጊም) ፈጺሙ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ስለዚ እዚ ንምንታይ ከምኡ ምዃኑ ኣብ ሓደ ፍሉይ ደብዳቤ ግለጽ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "ወለዲ", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ምስ በዓልቲ-ቤትካ ከም ዝተመርዓኻ ወይ ምስ መጻምድትኻ ብሓባር ትነብር ከም ዝነበርካ ዘርእዩ ሰነዳት።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቕጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን ናይ ስድራቤት መንበሪ ካርድ ናይ ልደት ምስክር ወረቐት ናይ ልደት ምዝገባ ክብረ-መዝገብ ናይ ጥምቀት ምስክር ወረቐት ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "(ደጊም) ፈጺሙ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ስለዚ እዚ ንምንታይ ከምኡ ምዃኑ ኣብ ሓደ ፍሉይ ደብዳቤ ግለጽ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "(ተናበይቲ) ቆልዑት ወይ ኣሕዋት/ኣሓት", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ቆልዑት ወይ ኣሕዋትን ኣሓትን ከምዘለዉኻ ዘርእዩ ሰነዳት።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቕጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን ናይ ስድራቤት መንበሪ ካርድ ናይ ልደት ምስክር ወረቐት ናይ ልደት ምዝገባ ክብረ-መዝገብ ናይ ጥምቀት ምስክር ወረቐት መግለጺ ሞግዚትነት (ምጽዳቕ ሞግዚትነት)", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "(ደጊም) ፈጺሙ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ስለዚ እዚ ንምንታይ ከምኡ ምዃኑ ኣብ ሓደ ፍሉይ ደብዳቤ ግለጽ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "ዝሞተ ወላዲ(ወለዲ) ናይ (ተናባዩ) ቆልዓ", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ነዞም ሰነዳት ኣተሓሒዝካ ክትልእኮም ዘለካ፣ እቲ ወላዲ (ወለዲ) ናይቲ (ተናባዪ) ቆልዓ ዝሞተ ምስ ዝኸውን ጥራይ እዩ።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቕጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ሰነድ የለን ናይ ሞት ምስክር ወረቐት ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "(ደጊም) ፈጺሙ ሰነዳት የብልካን ድዩ? ስለዚ እዚ ንምንታይ ከምኡ ምዃኑ ኣብ ሓደ ፍሉይ ደብዳቤ ግለጽ።", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "ወተሃደራዊ ኣገልግሎት", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "ኣባል ስድራ-ቤትካ ኣብ ወተሃደራዊ ኣገልግሎት ከም ዘሎ ወይ ከም ዝነበረ ዘርእዩ ሰነዳት።", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ብቕጥታ እኹል 2. መብዛሕትኡ ግዜ ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ 3. ተወሳኺ መርመራ የድሊ ወይ እኹል ኣይኮነን ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን ወተሃደራዊ መለለዪ መንነት ናይ ሃገራዊ ኣገልግሎት ምስክር ወረቐት ናይ ምጥያስ ምስክር ወረቐት ኣብዚ ጉጅለ ዝምደቡ ሰነዳት የለዉን", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Somalia (Soomaaliya)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "La soo gudbi kaliya nuqullo dokumentiyada ah codsigaaga. Waa inaad soo dirtaa dokumentiyada asalka ah markii ay IND helaan codsigaaga. Waxaad kadib warqad ka heleysaa (qirashada rasiidka) oo ay weheliso lifaaq kaa codsanaya inaad soo dirto dokumentiyada asalka ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Aqoonsiga", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Dokumentiyada lagu cadeynayo aqoonsiga xubinta qoyskaaga.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Caadiyan isla markiiba si ku filan 2. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa badanaa loo baahanyahay 3. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa loo baahanyahay ama aan ku filneyn Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Baasaboorka Kaarkaqoonsiga Xaqiijinta aqooa nsiga Bayaan ka soo baxay maamulada Shatiga darawalnimada", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Miyaadan haysan wax dokumentiyo ah gabi ahaanba (hadda)? Haddii ay sidaas tahay, ku sharax sababta warqad gooni ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Xaas ama lammaane", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Dokumentiyada lagu muujinayo inaad xaas tahay ama aad la wada nooleydeen lamaanahaaga.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Caadiyan isla markiiba si ku filan 2. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa badanaa loo baahanyahay 3. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa loo baahanyahay ama aan ku filneyn Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Shahaadada guurka Cadeynta inaad wada nooleydeen Sawirada arooskiina", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Miyaadan haysan wax dokumentiyo ah gabi ahaanba (hadda)? Haddii ay sidaas tahay, ku sharax sababta warqad gooni ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Waalidiinta", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Dokumentiyada cadeynaya inaad tahay canugga waalidiintaada.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Caadiyan isla markiiba si ku filan 2. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa badanaa loo baahanyahay 3. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa loo baahanyahay ama aan ku filneyn Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Shahaadada dhalashada Warqad laga soo saaray diiwaanka dhalashada", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Miyaadan haysan wax dokumentiyo ah gabi ahaanba (hadda)? Haddii ay sidaas tahay, ku sharax sababta warqad gooni ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "(Koriin) caruur ama walaalo gabdho/wiilal ah", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Dokumentiyada muujinaya inaad leedahay carruur (koriin) ah ama walaalo gabdho/wiilal ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Caadiyan isla markiiba si ku filan 2. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa badanaa loo baahanyahay 3. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa loo baahanyahay ama aan ku filneyn Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Shahaadada dhalashada Warqad laga soo saaray diiwaanka dhalashada Canuga la korinayo ama la korsado: Ku dhawaaqida korsashada / ku dhawaaqida masuuliyada ee ka soo baxday maxkamada", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Miyaadan haysan wax dokumentiyo ah gabi ahaanba (hadda)? Haddii ay sidaas tahay, ku sharax sababta warqad gooni ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Waalidka (waalidiinta) dhintay ee canugga (korsashada)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Waxaad u baahantahay oo kaliya inaad soo dirto dokumentiyadaan ku saabsan waalidka (waalidiinta) dhintay ee canugga (la korsaday).", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Caadiyan isla markiiba si ku filan 2. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa badanaa loo baahanyahay 3. Baaris dheeri ah ayaa loo baahanyahay ama aan ku filneyn Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Wax dokumenti ah kuma jiraan kooxdaan Shahaadada dhimashada", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Miyaadan haysan wax dokumentiyo ah gabi ahaanba (hadda)? Haddii ay sidaas tahay, ku sharax sababta warqad gooni ah.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Yemen (اليمن)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "عند تقديم طلبك، أرسل نسخًا فقط من المستندات. يجب عليك إرسال المستندات الأصلية بعد أن تتلقى دائرة الهجرة والتجنيس (IND) طلبك. بعد ذلك ستتلقى رسالة (تأكيد استلام) مرفقة بتعليمات حول كيفية إرسال المستندات الأصلية.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "الهوية", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُثبت هوية أحد أفراد عائلتك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة بطاقة الهوية (ابتداء من سن 16 سنة) رخصة القيادة جواز السفر", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الزوج أو شريك الحياة", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أنك متزوج أو أنك عشت مع شريكك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة دليل على أنك كنت تعيش مع شريكك صور من حفل الزواج لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة عقد زواج نسخة من عقد زواج", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الوالدان", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أنك ابن أو ابنة والديك.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة تصريح من السفارة مستخرج من سجل المواليد مستخرج من سجلّ العائلة دفتر العائلة شهادة الميلاد إذا ولد الطفل في بلد آخر غير اليمن: نسخة من شهادة الميلاد", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الأطفال (أو الأطفال تحت الوصاية) أو الإخوة والأخوات", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أن لديك أطفالًا (تحت الوصاية) أو إخوة وأخوات.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة بالنسبة للطفل تحت الوصاية: تصريح من السفارة وثيقة التبنّي / وثيقة الوصاية من المحكمة مستخرج من السجلّ العائلي مستخرج من سجلّ المواليد بطاقة عائلية دفتر العائلة شهادة ميلاد إذا ولد الطفل في بلد آخر غير اليمن: نسخة من شهادة الميلاد", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "أحد الوالدين أو كلاهما متوفّيان للطفل (أو الطفل تحت الوصاية)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "لا تحتاج إلى إرسال هذه الوثائق إلا في حال كان أحد الوالدين أو كلاهما متوفّيان للطفل (أو للطفل تحت الوصاية).", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة شهادة الوفاة نسخة من شهادة الوفاة", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "لا تتوفر (لم تعد لديك) على وثائق من المجموعة 1؟ أو لم تعد لديك أي وثائق على الإطلاق؟ اشرح في رسالة منفصلة سبب ذلك.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "الخدمة العسكرية", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "الوثائق التي تُظهر أن أحد أفراد أسرتك يؤدي الخدمة العسكرية أو سبق له أداؤها.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3.  تتطلب هذه الوثائق بحثا إضافيا أو تُعدُّ غير كافية 2. غالبًا ما تحتاج هذه الوثائق إلى بحث إضافي 1. غالبًا ما تكون هذ الوثائق كافية مباشرة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة لا توجد وثائق أخرى في هذه المجموعة دفتر الخدمة العسكرية", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Afghanistan (افعانستان)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "در هنگام درخواست خود فقط کاپی اسناد را ارسال کنید. شما باید اسناد اصلی را بعد از آن کهIND درخواست شما را دریافت کرد، روان کنید. شما یک مکتوب (تصدیق دریافت) همراه با یک ضمیمه دریافت می‌کنید که توسط آن اسناد اصلی را ارسال خواهید کرد.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "هویت", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "اسنادی که هویت عضو خانوادهٔ شما را ثابت کند.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3 . ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضافی ضرورت است 1. معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند لایسنس دریوری ( گواهینامه رانندگی) تذکره الکترونیکی تذکره کاغذی لایسنس دریوری پاسپورت", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "اگر شما (دیگر) اسناد از گروه ۱ ندارید، یا هیچ سندی در دست ندارید، پس در یک مکتوب جداگانه توضیح بدهید که علت آن چیست؟", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "شوهر یا همسر (یا شریک زندگی)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "اسنادی که نشان بدهد شما با هم ازدواج (نکاح) کرده‌اید یا با شریک زندگی‌تان هم‌خانه بوده‌اید.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3. ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضافی 1. معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند ترجمه رسمی نکاح خط مدارکی که نشان بدهد شما با هم زندگی کرده‌اید. عکس از جشن عروسی یا مراسم عقد اگر هیچ سندی در این گروه نداشته باشد نکاح خط سند نکاح", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "اگر شما (دیگر) اسناد از گروه ۱ ندارید، یا هیچ سندی در دست ندارید، پس در یک مکتوب جداگانه توضیح بدهید که علت آن چیست؟", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "والدین (پدر و مادر)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "اسنادی که نشان بدهد شما فرزند (اولاد) والدین خود هستید..", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3. ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضاف ی ضرورت است 1. معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند هیچ اسنادی در این گروه (قسمت) نداشته باشید. برگهٔ راجستری تولد سند ولادت (تولد) کارت ثبت تولدات (کارت زرد رنگ)", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "اگر شما (دیگر) اسناد از گروه ۱ ندارید، یا هیچ سندی در دست ندارید، پس در یک مکتوب جداگانه توضیح بدهید که علت آن چیست؟", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "برادران و خواهران (اولاد تحت سرپرستی)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "اسنادی که نشان بدهد شما اولادی یا برادران و خواهرانی دارید", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "3. ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضافی ضرورت است 1. معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند برای فرزندخواندگی یا طفل تحت سرپرست اظهارنامه سفارت سند فرزندخواندگی / فیصله محکمه دربارهٔ حق سرپرستی برگهٔ راجستری تولد سند تولد یا تذکره کارت (زرد) ثبت تولدات", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "اگر شما (دیگر) اسناد از گروه ۱ ندارید، یا هیچ سندی در دست ندارید، پس در یک مکتوب جداگانه توضیح بدهید که علت آن چیست؟", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "والد یا والدین طفل (فرزندخوانده یا تحت سرپرستی) فوت‌شدهٔ", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "شما این اسناد را فقط در صورتی ضرورت است روان کنید که والد (یا والدین) طفل (فرزندخوانده یا تحت سرپرستی) فوت شده باشد.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضافی ضرورت است 1 . معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند هیچ اسنادی در این گروه (قسمت) نداشته باشید. هیچ اسنادی در این گروه (قسمت) نداشته باشید. سند فوت", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "اگر شما (دیگر) اسناد از گروه ۱ ندارید، یا هیچ سندی در دست ندارید، پس در یک مکتوب جداگانه توضیح بدهید که علت آن چیست؟", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "خدمت عسگری", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "سنادی که ثوبت بسازد عضو فامیل شما به خدمت عسگری رفته است.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "3. ضرورت به تحقیقات بیشتر است یا کفایت نمی‌کند 2. معمولاً به تحقیقات اضافی ضرورت است 1. معمولاً فوراً کفایت می‌کند هیچ اسنادی در این گروه (قسمت) نداشته باشید. هیچ اسنادی در این گروه (قسمت) نداشته باشید. کتابچه عسگری کارت عسگری", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Turkey (Türkiye)", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Başvurunuzda sadece belgelerin fotokopilerini gönderin. IND başvurunuzu aldıktan sonra orijinal belgeleri göndermeniz gerekir. Bu aşamada size bir mektup (alındı teyidi) ve orijinal belgeleri göndermeniz için bir ek belge gönderilir.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Kimlik", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Aile üyenizin kimliğini kanıtlamak için gereken belgeler.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Genellikle hemen yeterli olur 2. Genellikle ek araştırma gerekir 3. Ek araştırma gerekli veya yetersiz Pasaport Nüfus cüzdanı veya kimlik kartı Sürücü belgesi Nüfus kayıt örneği", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Grup 1’deki belgeleriniz artık yoksa veya elinizde hiç belge kalmadıysa, bunun nedenini ayrı bir dilekçede ayrıntılı şekilde açıklayın.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Eş veya partner", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Evlendiğinizi ya da partnerinizle birlikte yaşadığınızı göstermek için gereken belgeler.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Genellikle hemen yeterli olur 2. Genellikle ek araştırma gerekir 3. Ek araştırma gerekli veya yetersiz Aile cuzdanı Evlenme Kayıt Örneği (Formül B) Aile nüfus kayıt örneği Bu grupta belge bulunmamaktadır Bu grupta belge bulunmamaktadır", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Grup 1’den (artık) belgeleriniz yok mu? Veya hiç belgeniz yok mu? O halde bunun neden böyle olduğunu ayrı bir mektupta açıklayın.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Ebeveynler", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Anne babanızın çocuğu olduğunuzu gösteren belgeler.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Genellikle hemen yeterli olur 2. Genellikle ek araştırma gerekir 3. Ek araştırma gerekli veya yetersiz Doğum belgesi Aile nüfus kayıt örneği Doğum kayıt örneği Hastane doğum belgesi Bu grupta belge bulunmamaktadır", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Grup 1’den (artık) belgeleriniz yok mu? Yoksa hiç belgeniz yok mu? O halde bunun neden böyle olduğunu ayrı bir mektupta açıklayın.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "(Koruyucu ailedeki) çocuklar veya kardeşler", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Çocuğunuzun veya kardeşlerinizin olduğunu gösteren belgeler.", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "1. Genellikle hemen yeterli olur 2. Genellikle ek araştırma gerekir 3. Ek araştırma gerekli veya yetersiz Doğum belgesi Aile nüfus kayıt örneği Doğum kayıt örneği Evlat edinme belgesi Hastane doğum belgesi Vesayet belgesi Bu grupta belge bulunm