n) with an attachment to which you must send the original documents.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Identity", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Documents to prove the identity of your family member.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Passport Identity card (nüfus cüzdani or kimlik karti) Driver''s license (Sürücü belgesi) Extract from the population register (nüfus kayit örneği)", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Spouse or partner", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Documents to prove that you are married or have lived together with your partner.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Family booklet / Marriage booklet (Aile cuzdani) Marriage certificate (Evlenme Kayit Örne ği / Formul B) Family extract No documents in this group No documents in this group", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Parents", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Documents to prove that you are your parents child.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Birth certificate Family extract Birth extract Proof of birth from the hospital No documents in this group", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "(Foster)children or brothers/sisters", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Documents to prove that you have children or brothers or sisters.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Birth certificate Family extract Birth extract Adoption certificate Proof of birth from the hospital Guardianship declaration No documents in this group", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Deceased parent(s) of the (foster)child", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You only need to send these documents if the parent(s) of the (foster) child have died.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Death certificate Extract from the death register Death form No documents in this group", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Do you no longer have any documents from group 1? Or do you no longer have any documents at all? Then explain this in a separate letter.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Military service", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Documents to show that your family member is or has been in military service.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "1. Usually sufficient immediately 2. Usually additional research required 3. Additional research required or insufficient Military booklet Military ID card No documents in this group No documents in this group", "type": "Table"}, {"text": "Application forms", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You can submit this application online. Do you need to use both online application forms? Then first submit the online application for a \"provisional residence permit – persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker.\" Then submit the other application.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Online Application for a ''Regular Provisional Residence permit - persons making a journey in connection with family reunification with an asylum seeker''", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You were over 18 when you applied for asylum and are applying for your partner or (foster) child. Or you were under 18 and unaccompanied when you applied for asylum and are applying for your parent(s).", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Apply online", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Online Application for a ''Regular Provisional Residence permit - Family Reunification Asylum Art. 8 ECHR''", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "You want to apply for an mvv for other family members, such as brothers and sisters.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Apply online", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Written application forms", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Download a form if you prefer to fill in the application in writing and send it by post.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Application for a residence permit for asylum family reunification B07009E (PDF, 252.34 KB)", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appointment family reunification of refugees IND", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member must travel to the Netherlands within 90 days after collecting the MVV. After arriving in the Netherlands, your family member reports within 3 days to the IND. Registration is by appointment only. Does your family member need reception? Then the Central Agency for the Reception of Asylum Seekers (COA) will make this appointment for you.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Arrange reception COA", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Do you live in a reception centre from COA or NIDOS? Or you live in a place of residence that is not suitable for all of your family members to live in? Then you need to ask the COA for reception for your family member. You do this by e-mail. Ask for reception after the journey for your family member has been booked, but before they depart to the Netherlands.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Asking COA for reception by e-mail", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "This is how you ask the COA for reception for your family member:", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Send an e-mail to the COA in which you ask for reception for your family member. Send the e-mail to this e-mail address: FMMZZevenaarDuiven@coa.nl.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Put the following details in the e-mail:", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Your first and surname, your telephone number and e-mail address.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "The first names and surnames of all your traveling family members.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "The V-number of all your traveling family members.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Date of arrival in the Netherlands of your traveling family members. This is also the day your family members will need reception for the first time.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Within 2 working days you will receive a confirmation email from the COA saying where your reception is.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Appointment with the IND by COA", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Did you send an e-mail to the COA for reception? The COA will then make an appointment for you at the IND. You do not have to make an appointment yourself.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Make an appointment at IND when having a place of residence", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Make appointment", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Important information when making the appointment", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Only make an appointment if you have a suitable place of residence for all your family members. Do you not have a suitable place of residence? The COA will then make an appointment for you.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Only make an appointment after booking your family members’ journey to the Netherlands, but before their departure to the Netherlands.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Make an appointment for all family members who need to register at the IND. Fill out their V-numbers and first names and surnames.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Fill out your e-mail address or the e-mail address of your counsellor from VWN if you have one.", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Cancelling appointment", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "What if the appointment made cannot go through? For example, because your family member arrives in the Netherlands later than planned? Then cancel the appointment via the link in the e-mail confirming your appointment. As soon as this is possible, make a new appointment for your family member.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "The residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Find out what else you need to know about the residence permit:", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member will receive a derivative residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member will receive a derivative asylum residence permit. This means that the residence of your family member depends on your asylum residence permit. The IND can withdraw your family member’s residence permit if there is no longer a family relationship with you. For example, if your family member is a child who will go and live on their own within a year.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Your family member can apply for an independent asylum residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member may also apply for asylum in the Netherlands on their own. The IND then assesses whether your family member has a right to an independent asylum residence permit.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Working with the residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member may work in the Netherlands with a temporary derivative residence permit. Their employer does not need a work permit (in Dutch: tewerkstellingsvergunning or TWV). On the back of the residence permit it says ‘Free to work. Work permit is not required (in Dutch: Arbeid vrij toegestaan. TWV niet vereist).", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Legal obligations", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "A sponsor has an obligation to provide information and an administrative obligation. Your family member has an obligation to provide information. Read more about the legal obligations of the sponsor for a family member and the foreign national’s obligation to provide information.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "The IND checks whether you meet your obligations. Are you violating your obligations? You then may get an administrative fine.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Validity of the residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Your family member’s residence permit is valid for 5 years.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Type of residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "The residence permit is type III, temporary asylum residence permit.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Other applications", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Replacement of the residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Has your family member’s residence permit been damaged, lost or stolen? Then, have the residence permit replaced. Go to the page residence permit damaged or change of personal details or residence permit lost or stolen.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Extend the residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Will your family member’s residence permit expire soon? Then, your family member can extend the residence permit", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "Permanent residence permit", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Has your family member had a residence permit for 5 years? Then, your family member can apply for a permanent residence permit.", "type": "NarrativeText"}, {"text": "See also", "type": "Title"}, {"text": "Living in the Netherlands", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Travelling with a residence permit and a return visa", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Apply for asylum in the Netherlands", "type": "ListItem"}, {"text": "Video", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Requirements, process and costs", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Documents", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Application forms", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "Appointment family reunification of refugees IND", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "The residence permit", "type": "UncategorizedText"}, {"text": "See also", "type": "NarrativeText"}], "fetch_date": "2026-03-02"}', 'webpage', '2026-03-28 16:32:08.725204+00', '2026-03-28 16:25:32.781568+00', 'Asylum family reunification

