This proclaimer applies to the website ind.nl/en. This is the official website of the Dutch Immigration and Naturalisation Service (IND). The IND is part of the Ministry of Asylum and Migration. Via ind.nl/en we inform you in English about laws and regulations implemented by te IND.

Involved parties

Several parties are involved with this website:

Assignment client responsible entity in terms of policy: Ministry of Asylum and Migration

Management and editing: Immigration and Naturalisation service (IND)

Use of the website

We do our best to always provide correct and up to date information. However, it is possible that certain information is not completely correct or up to date. Do you see information that you think is incorrect or outdated? Please contact the IND. We appreciate your feedback. If necessary, we can adjust the information or remove any unclarities. Reuse of content is allowed, if you mention the source.'),
